To install the debian-Package you need a debian sarge system, 
i.e. sarge or knoppix 3.4 or later


Installation:

1. Add in /etc/apt/sources.list the following line:


   # FOR PROBLECTIX
   deb http://cvs.bszleo.de/problectix/debs ./


2. apt-get update

3. apt-cache search problectix should show

   problectix
   usermin-problectix


4. Install problectix with

   apt-get install problectix


5. Install usermin-problectix

   apt-get install usermin-problectix


